# +------------------------------------------------------------------+
# | MARIADB BACKUP - AMAZON S3                                       |
# +------------------------------------------------------------------+
# | ENABLE_S3BACKUP : Backup MariaDB only to S3 True/False           |
# | S3POD           : S3 Bucket name - named after PoD               |
# | S3REGION        : Default Region                                 |
# | S3ENCRYPTPWD    : Encryption Password for Secret Transfer        |
